{"tid":1646992,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【憂求診被捕】美聯社訪「隱世診所」 義醫400港示威者","createTime":"2019-10-11T14:22:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-11T16:15:07.000Z","uid":30001,"like":29,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"16bac0e18bac03f13358c445b7093cdebe38a729","tid":1646992,"uid":30001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T14:22:00.000Z","msg":"Source: <a href=\"https://www.am730.com.hk/news/新聞/【不敢求診怕被捕】美聯社訪「隱世診所」-義醫400港示威者-191775\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.am730.com.hk%2Fnews%2F%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%2F%E3%80%90%E4%B8%8D%E6%95%A2%E6%B1%82%E8%A8%BA%E6%80%95%E8%A2%AB%E6%8D%95%E3%80%91%E7%BE%8E%E8%81%AF%E7%A4%BE%E8%A8%AA%E3%80%8C%E9%9A%B1%E4%B8%96%E8%A8%BA%E6%89%80%E3%80%8D-%E7%BE%A9%E9%86%AB400%E6%B8%AF%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E8%80%85-191775&d=6p%2BW5B2gHvlBGPj8iPYwcqcrr%2FRj6%2FCkFD6x6yFTuc4%3D&h=2672ad5d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.am730.com.hk/news/新聞/【不敢求診怕被捕】美聯社訪「隱世診所」-義醫400港示威者-191775</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n美聯社報道，本港不少反修例示威者在抗爭期間受傷後，因擔心在醫院被捕而不敢求醫，該社訪問了一群自稱「隱世診所」(Hidden Clinic)的義務醫療人員，指迄今已治療過多達400人，傷勢包括骨折、甩骹、裂開的傷口，以及長期吸入催淚煙導致咳血等，並指過去一周求診的示威者傷勢，較之前更為嚴重。<br />\n該組織成員包括一名在公立醫院任職的姓黃(音譯Wong)實習女醫生，她下班後會透過手機訊息及照片，為傷者作初步診斷，然後聯同其他義務醫生安排治療。她稱，早在示威剛開始時，已有上前線醫治示威者，及至7月底加入「隱世診所」，因為「我見到他們(示威者)的傷勢愈來愈嚴重」。她說，「<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">政府公布的(傷者人數)資料不再準確，因為有非常多的隱藏個案&hellip;&hellip;他們寧願忍痛，也不想(在醫院)被捕</span></strong>」。<br />\n示威者頸部疑中橡膠子彈  吞嚥困難<br />\n黃醫生舉例稱，組織在周一凌晨接到一個案，可見一名示威者頸部<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">有個大如布冧的圓形傷口，邊緣呈黑色，似中了橡膠子彈</span></strong>，她指該名示威者二十多歲，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">受傷後吞嚥亦有困難</span></strong>，幸組織找到一名私人外科醫生，在其診所醫治傷者；當晚尚有一名22歲示威者手臂骨折、另有兩人需縫針。<br />\n報道指，類似的義務醫療組織不止「隱世診所」一個。一名女中醫師向美聯社稱，她迄今已治療過60至80人，部分是被催淚彈及警方發射的其他鎮暴武器所傷，她表示︰「對於我們這種不敢上街的一群，最起碼能做的是醫好他們(示威者)的傷勢。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tKzRTfB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtKzRTfB.png&h=9b35b86c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UvCcCHi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUvCcCHi.png&h=c032897a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ebee9e3ca7b77d94f95d3cb1e3524cddf181fa86","tid":1646992,"uid":265339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T14:25:27.000Z","msg":"感激醫護<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n突發！香城online現已公開發售！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1646714\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1646714</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"b9fe348bf4efbbb0d6b517b92638760d42cb08c8","tid":1646992,"uid":30001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T14:27:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52e2613f0b396177e879876a9674fa63ac5f8fb7","tid":1646992,"uid":127611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T14:28:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"125f7a335edcdc8bf0162b167ea35665005025d7","tid":1646992,"uid":259329,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T14:29:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bc6c6a129f2a34e5fa2c69781e8c716a3be0b80b","tid":1646992,"uid":66954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T14:38:15.000Z","msg":"好人一生平安"},{"pid":"15b13b719eea15cc23435afaa2a616934c8259eb","tid":1646992,"uid":48868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T14:41:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c76b13d4449328d3a41e037a8ce661369545e4ee","tid":1646992,"uid":30001,"like":2,"dislike